ional/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E7%BD%AA-%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E5%AE%98%E5%BA%B7%E6%98%8E%E5%87%B1%E4%BB%8A%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E9%96%89%E9%96%80%E5%AF%A9%E8%A8%8A-%E5%A6%BB-%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A4%E6%9C%89%E7%BD%AA/</a><br />\n<br />\n被控間諜罪的加拿大前外交官康明凱（Michael Kovrig）今日於北京第二中級人民法院閉門受審。包括加拿大、美國在內共 28 個駐華使館外交官今早去到法院外希望入內聽審，但被拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大駐華使館公使倪傑民（Jim Nickel）向法院外的傳媒表示，審訊已經開始，但北京當局以案件涉及國家機密為由，拒絕一眾外交官入內旁聽。今日到來的駐華使館外交官多達 28 人，來自 26 個國家，除美加之外，還有英國、德國、澳洲、荷蘭和捷克等。<br />\n<br />\n站在倪傑民旁邊的美國駐華使館公使柯有為（William Klein）表示，美國國務卿布林肯已表明，會協助康明凱及同樣被控間諜罪於上周五受審的加拿大商人邁克爾斯帕弗（Michael Spavor），美國將視二人一如美國公民。一名不願透露身份的外交官向路透社表示，今天到來的外交人員是要展示團結，表明任意拘留是絕對不可接受。"},{"pid":"cc4fff58a048a0903179c8b1ffd6bddb610e42bd","tid":2456617,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:32:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/janisfrayer/status/1373861954930892803?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjanisfrayer%2Fstatus%2F1373861954930892803%3Fs%3D21&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbZhvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=ed6ee95c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjanisfrayer%2Fstatus%2F1373861954930892803%3Fs%3D21&h=1b8f8b91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/janisfrayer/status/1373861954930892803?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n名單有：<br />\n#China refused to let Canada, U.S., Norway, Spain, U.K., Finland, Lithuania, Sweden, Netherlands, Estonia, Ireland,Czech Rep., Switzerland, France, Germany, Austria, N.Z., Belgium,Latvia, Australia, Italy, EU, Denmark, Romania &amp; Latvia into #MichaelKovrig&rsquo;s trial @NBCNews"},{"pid":"cfa67d44ca1d2c0c1232d429d72029d355179953","tid":2456617,"uid":298523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:34:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50294b7170db21190fea877913366c3776a50632","tid":2456617,"u